<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Airpax - Ticket Cancellation Email</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        .email-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h2 {
            color: #2a9d8f;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .details-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .details-table th,
        .details-table td {
            text-align: left;
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        .details-table th {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            color: #333;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: black;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .footer table {
            text-align: center;

        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="email-container">
        <h2>Ticket Canellation Request</h2>
        <p>Dear <strong>
                <%= user.name %>
            </strong>,</p>
        <p>We are writing to inform you that your cancellation request for the following ticket has been successfully
            confirmed.</p>

        <h3>Trip Details:</h3>
        <table class="details-table">
            <tr>
                <th>From</th>
                <td>
                    <%= trip.from %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>To</th>
                <td>
                    <%= trip.to %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>JourneyStartDate</th>
                <td>
                    <%= trip.journeystartdate %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>JourneyEndDate</th>
                <td>
                    <%= trip.journeyenddate %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>JourneyStartTime</th>
                <td>
                    <%= trip.starttime %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>JourneyEndTime</th>
                <td>
                    <%= trip.endtime %>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <h3>Ticket Information:</h3>
        <table class="details-table">
            <tr>
                <th>PNR Number</th>
                <td><strong>
                        <%= pnr %>
                    </strong></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Refund Amount</th>
                <td>
                    <%= amount %>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Cancellation Reason </th>
                <td>
                    <%= reason %>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <h3>Passenger Details :</h3>
        <% seat.forEach(function(seat) { %>
            <table class="details-table">
                <tr>
                    <th>First Name</th>
                    <td>
                        <%=seat.details.fname %>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Last Name</th>
                    <td>
                        <%=seat.details.lname %>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Age</th>
                    <td>
                        <%=seat.details.age %>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Gender</th>
                    <td>
                        <%=seat.details.gender %>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Seat No</th>
                    <td>
                        <%=seat.details.seatNo %>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Amount</th>
                    <td>
                        <%=seat.details.amount %>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <% }); %>

                <p>If you need any further assistance, please feel free to contact us at <a
                        href="mailto:info@airpax.co">info@airpax.co</a> or call us at <a
                        href="tel:+919990301111">+919990301111</a>. You can also visit our website <a
                        href="https://airpax.co/">Airpax</a> for more information.</p>

                <p>We wish you a pleasant and enjoyable trip!</p>

                <p>Best regards,</p>
                <p><strong>Airpax</strong></p>

                <div class="footer">
                    <p> <strong>RIGI TRANS TECH PVT LTD</strong></p>
                    <tr>
                        <td>PERNAM INN</td>
                        <td> 837/1</td>
                    </tr><br>
                    <tr>
                        <td>MANDI ESTATE</td>
                        <td>NEW DELHI</td>
                    </tr><br>
                    <tr>
                        <td>110047</td>
                    </tr>

                    <p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@airpax.co">info@airpax.co</a> | Phone: <a
                            href="tel:+919990301111">+919990301111</a></p>
                    <p><a href="https://airpax.co/">airpax.co</a></p>
                </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>